room_title: Escape room "Tiki Island" by EscapeQuest in Chicago
room_description: You, along with your fellow research team members, are being sent to a remote island in the South Pacific. Your Professor, who had been researching volcanic activity on Tiki Island, hasn't been heard from in a few weeks. You need to search his mysterious and deserted hut built near the base of an active volcano. Can your group finish your beloved professor's research before the volcano erupts?
